{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-jsx","path":"/deep-js-8/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"ocean.dev"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"0376d6f2-f085-5524-b81f-3d30a3fe9bb1","excerpt":"제어문 개요 제어문은 조건에 따라 코드 블록을 실행(조건문)하거나 반복실행(반복문)할 때 사용한다. 제어문은 코드의 실행 흐름을 인위적으로 제어할 수 있다. → 순자적으로 진행하는 직관적인 코드의 흐름을 혼란스럽게 만든다. 즉, 제어문은 코드의 흐름을 이해하기 어렵게 만들어 가독성을 해치는 단점 이 있다. → 가독성이 좋지 않은 코드는 오류를 발생시키는 …","html":"<h3 id=\"제어문-개요\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%9C%EC%96%B4%EB%AC%B8-%EA%B0%9C%EC%9A%94\" aria-label=\"제어문 개요 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>제어문 개요</h3>\n<hr>\n<blockquote>\n<p>제어문은 조건에 따라 코드 블록을 실행(조건문)하거나 반복실행(반복문)할 때 사용한다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>제어문은 코드의 실행 흐름을 인위적으로 제어할 수 있다. → 순자적으로 진행하는 직관적인 코드의 흐름을 혼란스럽게 만든다.</li>\n<li>즉, 제어문은 코드의 흐름을 이해하기 어렵게 만들어 가독성을 해치는 단점 이 있다. → 가독성이 좋지 않은 코드는 오류를 발생시키는 원인</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"c\"><pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token function\">forEach</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token function\">map</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token function\">filter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token function\">reduce</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n같은 <span class=\"token string\">\"고차 함수\"</span>를 사용한 <span class=\"token string\">\"함수형 프로그래밍 기법\"</span>에서는 제어문의 사용을 억제하여 복잡성을 해결하려고 노력한다<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"81-블록문\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#81-%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9D%EB%AC%B8\" aria-label=\"81 블록문 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>8.1 블록문</h3>\n<hr>\n<p>블록문은 0개 이상의 문을 중괄호로 묶은 것.</p>\n<p><strong>특징</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>언제나 문(statement)의 종료를 의미하는 자체 종결성을 갖기 때문에 세미콜론을 붙이지 않는다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cs\"><pre class=\"language-cs\"><code class=\"language-cs\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token class-name\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span></span> foo <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"82-조건문\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#82-%EC%A1%B0%EA%B1%B4%EB%AC%B8\" aria-label=\"82 조건문 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>8.2 조건문</h3>\n<hr>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">if..else</code> 와 <code class=\"language-text\">switch</code>문으로 제공한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"821-ifelse\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#821-ifelse\" aria-label=\"821 ifelse permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>8.2.1 if...else</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>if문의 조건식은 boolean 값으로 평가되어야 한다.</li>\n<li>코드 블록 내에의 문이 하나뿐이라면 중괄호를 생략할 수 있다.</li>\n<li>삼항 조건 연산자로 바꿔 쓸 수 있고, 삼항 연산자는 값으로 평가되는 표현식이다. 따라서 변수로 할당할 수 있다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cs\"><pre class=\"language-cs\"><code class=\"language-cs\"><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>조건식<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>num <span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> kind <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"양수\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 조건에 따라 단순히 값을 결정하여 변수에 할당하는 경우 삼항 조건 연산자를 사용하는 편이 가독성이 좋다.</span>\n<span class=\"token class-name\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span></span> kind <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> num <span class=\"token punctuation\">?</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>num <span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">?</span> '양수' <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> '음수'<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token char\">'명'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"822-switch\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#822-switch\" aria-label=\"822 switch permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>8.2.2 switch</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>switch문은 주어진 표현식을 평가하여 그 값과 일치하는 표현식을 갖는 case문으로 실행 흐름을 옮긴다.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">if...else</code> 조건식: boolean값으로 평가</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">switch</code> 표현식: 문자열이나 숫자값인 경우가 많음</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>💡폴스루(fall through)</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>문을 실행한 후 switch문을 탈출하지 않고 모든 case와 default문을 실행하는 것</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>기본적으로 case문에는 break문을 추가해야 한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>break 문을 생략한 폴스루가 유용한 경우</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>여러개의 case문을 하나의 조건으로 사용하기</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cs\"><pre class=\"language-cs\"><code class=\"language-cs\"><span class=\"token comment\">// 윤년 계산</span>\nswtich <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>month<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">case</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">case</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">case</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">case</span> <span class=\"token number\">7</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">case</span> <span class=\"token number\">8</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">case</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">case</span> <span class=\"token number\">12</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n\t\tdays <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">31</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token keyword\">break</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">case</span> <span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">case</span> <span class=\"token number\">6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">case</span> <span class=\"token number\">9</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">case</span> <span class=\"token number\">11</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n\t\tdays <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">30</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token keyword\">break</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">case</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n\t\tdays <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>year <span class=\"token operator\">%</span> <span class=\"token number\">4</span> <span class=\"token operator\">==</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span> <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> year <span class=\"token operator\">%</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span> <span class=\"token operator\">!=</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>year <span class=\"token operator\">%</span> <span class=\"token number\">400</span> <span class=\"token operator\">==</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">?</span> <span class=\"token number\">29</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">28</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token keyword\">break</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">default</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n\t\tconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Invaild month\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>case, default, break등 다양한 키워드를 사용해야 하고, 폴스루가 발생하는 등 문법도 목잡하다.</li>\n<li>따라서 <code class=\"language-text\">if..else</code>문으로 해결할 수 있다면 <code class=\"language-text\">switch</code>문 보다 <code class=\"language-text\">if..else</code>문을 사용하는 편이 좋다.</li>\n<li>조건식이 너무 많아서 가독성이 떨어지는 경우 <code class=\"language-text\">switch</code>를 사용한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"83-반복문-loop-statement\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#83-%EB%B0%98%EB%B3%B5%EB%AC%B8-loop-statement\" aria-label=\"83 반복문 loop statement permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>8.3 반복문 (loop statement)</h3>\n<hr>\n<ul>\n<li>자바스크립트는 <code class=\"language-text\">for</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">while</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">do..while</code>문을 제공한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>💡반복문을 대체할 수 있는 다양한 기능</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">forEach</code>: 배열을 순회할 때 사용</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">for..in</code>: 객체의 프로퍼티를 열거할 때 사용</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">for..of</code>: ES6에서 도입된 이터러블을 순회할 수 있음</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"831-for-문\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#831-for-%EB%AC%B8\" aria-label=\"831 for 문 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>8.3.1 for 문</h3>\n<p>for문은 조건식이 거짓으로 평가될 때까지 코드 블록을 반복 실행한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"c\"><pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token keyword\">for</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>변수 선언문 또는 할당문<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> 조건식<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> 증감식<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  조건식이 참인 경우 반복 실행될 문<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><figure class='gatsby-resp-image-figure' style='margin-bottom: 16px;'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 680px; '>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/static/5cc3daef3e8c20b415ad8be738732d4b/74cb2/image.png' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 61.76470588235294%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='for문의 실행순서' title='' src='/static/5cc3daef3e8c20b415ad8be738732d4b/ca1dc/image.png' srcset='/static/5cc3daef3e8c20b415ad8be738732d4b/e7570/image.png 170w,\n/static/5cc3daef3e8c20b415ad8be738732d4b/f46e7/image.png 340w,\n/static/5cc3daef3e8c20b415ad8be738732d4b/ca1dc/image.png 680w,\n/static/5cc3daef3e8c20b415ad8be738732d4b/02d09/image.png 1020w,\n/static/5cc3daef3e8c20b415ad8be738732d4b/9d567/image.png 1360w,\n/static/5cc3daef3e8c20b415ad8be738732d4b/74cb2/image.png 1450w' sizes='(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class='gatsby-resp-image-figcaption'>for문의 실행순서</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cs\"><pre class=\"language-cs\"><code class=\"language-cs\"><span class=\"token number\">1</span>️⃣ <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span>문을 실행하면 먼저 변수선언문 <span class=\"token class-name\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span></span> i <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span>이 실행된다<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n변수 선언문은 단 한 번만 실행된다<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n\n<span class=\"token number\">2</span>️⃣ 변수 선언문의 실행이 종료되면 조건식이 실행된다<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n현재 i 변수의 값은 <span class=\"token number\">0</span>이므로 조건식의 평가 결과는 <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span>다<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n\n<span class=\"token number\">3</span>️⃣ 조건식의 평가 결과가 <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span>이므로 코드 블록이 실행된다<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n증감문으로 실행 흐름이 이동하는 것이 아니라 코드 블록으로 실행 흐름이 이동하는 것에 주의하자<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n\n<span class=\"token number\">4</span>️⃣ 코드 블록의 실행이 종료되면 증감식 i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span>가 실행되어 i 변수의 값은 <span class=\"token number\">1</span>이 된다<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n\n<span class=\"token number\">5</span>️⃣ 증감식 실행이 종료되면 다시 조건식이 실행된다<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n변수 선언문이 실행되는 것이 아니라 조건식이 실행된다는 점에 주의하자\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>앞에서 설명했지만 변수 선언문은 단 한 번만 실행된다<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n현재 i 변수의 값은 <span class=\"token number\">1</span>이므로 조건식의 평가 결과는 <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span>다<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>for문의 변수 선언문, 조건식, 증감식은 모두 옵션이므로 반드시 사용할 필요는 없다.</li>\n<li>단, 어떤 식도 선언하지 않으면 무한루프가 된다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"c\"><pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//무한루프</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"832-while-문\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#832-while-%EB%AC%B8\" aria-label=\"832 while 문 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>8.3.2 while 문</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>주어진 조건식의 평가 결과가 참이면 코드 블록을 계속해서 반복 실행한다.</li>\n<li>while문은 조건문의 평가 결과가 거짓이 되면 코드 블록을 실행하지 않고 종료한다.</li>\n<li>무한 루프에서 탈출하기 위해서는 코드 블록 내에 <code class=\"language-text\">if</code>문으로 탈출 조건을 만들고 <code class=\"language-text\">break</code>문으로 탈출한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"c\"><pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token keyword\">while</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>true<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  count<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>count <span class=\"token operator\">==</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">break</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"833-dowhile-문\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#833-dowhile-%EB%AC%B8\" aria-label=\"833 dowhile 문 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>8.3.3 do...while 문</h3>\n<p>코드 블록을 먼저 실행하고 조건식을 평가한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cs\"><pre class=\"language-cs\"><code class=\"language-cs\"><span class=\"token comment\">// count가 3보다 작을 때까지 코드 블록을 반복 실행한다.</span>\n\n<span class=\"token class-name\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span></span> count <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">do</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>count<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 0 1 2</span>\n  count <span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">while</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>count <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"84-break문\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#84-break%EB%AC%B8\" aria-label=\"84 break문 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>8.4 break문</h3>\n<hr>\n<ul>\n<li>레이블 문, 반복문, 또는 switch 문의 코드블록을 탈출한다. 이 외의 블록에 break문을 사용하면 SyntaxError가 발생한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>❓레이블문</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>식별자가 붙은 문</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cs\"><pre class=\"language-cs\"><code class=\"language-cs\"><span class=\"token comment\">// foo라는 레이블 식별자가 붙은 레이블 문</span>\nfoo<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>'foo'<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>프로그램의 실행 순서를 제어하는 데 사용한다.</li>\n<li>switch문의 <code class=\"language-text\">case</code>문과 <code class=\"language-text\">default</code>문도 레이블 문이다.</li>\n<li>레이블 문을 탈출하려면 break문에 레이블 식별자를 지정한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cs\"><pre class=\"language-cs\"><code class=\"language-cs\">foo<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">break</span> foo<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>내부 for문에서 break문을 실행하면 탈출하여 외부 for문으로 진입한다.</li>\n<li>내부 for문이 아닌 <code class=\"language-text\">외부 for문을 탈출하려면</code> 레이블 문을 사용한다</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cs\"><pre class=\"language-cs\"><code class=\"language-cs\">outer<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>i <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> j <span class=\"token operator\">==</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">break</span> outer<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>레이블 문은 중첩된 for 문 외부로 탈출 할 때 유용하지만 그 외에는 일반적으로 권장하지 않는다.</li>\n<li>레이블 문 사용시 → 프로그램의 흐름이 복잡해져서 가독성이 나빠지고 오류를 발생시킬 가능성이 높아지기 때문 ( 존재 정도만 인지할 것 )</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"85-Continue-문\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#85-Continue-%EB%AC%B8\" aria-label=\"85 Continue 문 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>8.5 Continue 문</h3>\n<hr>\n<blockquote>\n<p>continue 문 은 반복문의 코드 블록 실행을 현 시점에서 중단하고 ,\n반복문의 증감식으로 실행 흐름을 이동시킨다. ( break 문처럼 반복문을 탈출하지는 않는다. )</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cs\"><pre class=\"language-cs\"><code class=\"language-cs\"><span class=\"token comment\">// for (var i = 0; i &lt; string.length; i++) {</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// search값이 아니면 현 지점에서 실행을 중단하고 반복문의 증감식으로 이동한다.</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">!=</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span> search<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">continue</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  count<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// continue문이 실행되면 이 문은 실행되지 않는다.</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>if 문 내에서 <code class=\"language-text\">실행해야 할 코드가 길다면</code> → <code class=\"language-text\">들여쓰기가 한 단계 더 깊어지므로</code> , continue 문을 사용하는 편이 가독성이 더 좋을 수 있다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cs\"><pre class=\"language-cs\"><code class=\"language-cs\"><span class=\"token comment\">// if문 내에서 여러 코드 작성해야 할 경우 -> continue 문을 사용하지 않았을 경우</span>\n<span class=\"token class-name\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span></span> arr <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token class-name\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span></span> target <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token class-name\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span></span> count <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span></span> i <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> arr<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// arr[i] 가 target 이하라면 count 증감</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>arr<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;=</span> target<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    count<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// code...</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// code...</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// code...</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// if문 내에서 여러 코드 작성해야 할 경우 -> continue 문을 사용한 경우 -> depth가 하나 줄어들었다.</span>\n<span class=\"token class-name\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span></span> arr <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token class-name\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span></span> target <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token class-name\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span></span> count <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span></span> i <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> arr<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// arr[i] 가 target 초과이면 count 증감하지 않는다.</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>arr<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">></span> target<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">continue</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  count<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// code...</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// code...</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// code...</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"8. 제어문(Control flow statement)","date":"August 05, 2024","update":"August 05, 2024","tags":["Javascript"],"series":"모던 자바스크립트 Deep Dive"},"fields":{"slug":"/deep-js-8/","readingTime":{"minutes":10.44}}},"seriesList":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"0f1a2f58-f0a9-551f-a3af-8313370fd034","fields":{"slug":"/deep-js-0/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"0. 프로그래밍"}}},{"node":{"id":"29f780e8-ee3e-58f9-94d1-7d65223be027","fields":{"slug":"/deep-js-1/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"1. 자바스크립트의 기본 개념과 동작원리"}}},{"node":{"id":"300acb14-db5c-57a2-a557-c5569308b991","fields":{"slug":"/deep-js-2/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"2. 자바스크립트 개발 환경과 실행 방법"}}},{"node":{"id":"3c8acf66-3cdd-511c-b852-adbc4d17e6bb","fields":{"slug":"/deep-js-4/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"4. 변수(Variable)"}}},{"node":{"id":"564da37b-b3d6-532f-8046-f1f1c494d18a","fields":{"slug":"/deep-js-5/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"5. 표현식과 문(Expression, Statement)"}}},{"node":{"id":"997615c1-0020-5443-ac34-1148e2930599","fields":{"slug":"/deep-js-6/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"6. 데이터 타입"}}},{"node":{"id":"0dfe45a9-0b33-517c-a55c-f5f5c8b28140","fields":{"slug":"/deep-js-7/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"7. 연산자(Operator)"}}},{"node":{"id":"0376d6f2-f085-5524-b81f-3d30a3fe9bb1","fields":{"slug":"/deep-js-8/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"8. 제어문(Control flow statement)"}}},{"node":{"id":"edd87130-aec4-5180-952d-01faf33d160e","fields":{"slug":"/deep-js-9/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"9. 타입 변환과 단축 평가(Type Coercion)"}}},{"node":{"id":"cc019850-07c7-59bc-b7ec-f6562d751ba8","fields":{"slug":"/deep-js-10/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"10. 객체 리터럴 (Object Literal)"}}},{"node":{"id":"a95a6396-75bf-573d-880b-b619202c1d7d","fields":{"slug":"/deep-js-11/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"11. 원시 값과 객체의 비교 (Primitive Type & Object Type)"}}},{"node":{"id":"51f94968-bc6e-5235-bd2e-b8e12d50d0e5","fields":{"slug":"/deep-js-12/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"12. 함수 (Function)"}}},{"node":{"id":"66b416d5-9ae6-5e60-a06d-93e0501fa8ce","fields":{"slug":"/deep-js-13/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"13. 스코프 (Scope)"}}},{"node":{"id":"77d054f4-7aad-5917-b811-d88bdf6b3d36","fields":{"slug":"/deep-js-14/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"14. 전역 변수의 문제점(Global Value)"}}},{"node":{"id":"4e72686f-e9c0-508e-9b62-44c12796616b","fields":{"slug":"/deep-js-15/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"15. let, const 키워드와 블록 레벨 스코프"}}},{"node":{"id":"0fcfe3e2-8d80-5338-b427-3b8a15f1c38a","fields":{"slug":"/deep-js-16/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"16. 프로퍼티 어트리뷰트(Property Attribute)"}}},{"node":{"id":"9a40f0b5-fd68-5c12-aa88-e1d58ef73117","fields":{"slug":"/deep-js-17/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"17. 생성자 함수에 의한 객체 생성(Constructor Function)"}}},{"node":{"id":"9dee99d7-74b6-57d7-b712-f4758729e5da","fields":{"slug":"/deep-js-18/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"18. 함수와 일급 객체(Function & First Class Object"}}},{"node":{"id":"3ba77c47-33d6-575f-86db-78267cd573cb","fields":{"slug":"/prototype-1/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"19. 프로토타입 (Prototype) (1)"}}},{"node":{"id":"b96c5de2-54e5-5139-8026-4b7c0d9e11b7","fields":{"slug":"/prototype-2/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"19. 프로토타입 (Prototype) (2)"}}},{"node":{"id":"e040841c-6725-5ae4-800d-77c1e2ff8d80","fields":{"slug":"/prototype-3/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"19. 프로토타입 (Prototype) (3)"}}},{"node":{"id":"1b6d17bd-8826-52c9-9827-d9e571c174d7","fields":{"slug":"/deep-js-20/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"20. strict mode"}}},{"node":{"id":"e076f928-82ca-5782-bd0b-d5a9f1193424","fields":{"slug":"/deep-js-21/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"21. 빌트인 객체 (Built in Object)"}}},{"node":{"id":"d5a056bb-3c94-5680-8d22-0256b8e9843e","fields":{"slug":"/deep-js-38/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"38. 브라우저의 렌더링 과정"}}}]},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/deep-js-7/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"7. 연산자(Operator)"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/deep-js-9/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"9. 타입 변환과 단축 평가(Type Coercion)"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"0376d6f2-f085-5524-b81f-3d30a3fe9bb1","series":"모던 자바스크립트 Deep Dive","previousPostId":"0dfe45a9-0b33-517c-a55c-f5f5c8b28140","nextPostId":"edd87130-aec4-5180-952d-01faf33d160e"}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}